snippet.title: TERE DIL MEIN - Rito Riba | Elvish Yadav & Jannat Zubair | Rajat Nagpal | Rana Sotal | Anshul Garg
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents Tere Dil Mein featuring Elvish Yadav & Jannat Zubair.

Audio Credits :-
Singer : Rito Riba
Music Composer : Rajat nagpal
Lyrics : Rana sotal

Lyrics :-
Rabb maan liya tujhko 
Jagg maan liya tujhko 
Tu he hai dunia meri 
Sabb maan liya tujhko,,

Maanga  jo paaya vahi  ,,

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

Bachkay ray bachkay deewane,,
Tu naino kay khel na jaane ,,


Tu meri jaan hai yaara ,,
Tu he hai jaan say pyara ,,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara
Dhadkan banke rehna yaara ,,
Apna mujhey kehna yaara ,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara ,

Tujhey yaar kahay
Jisay pyaar kahay 
Humey toh hogea hai vahi , 

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea ,,
khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

#teredilmein #elvishyadav #elvish #jannat #jannatzubair #ritoriba

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I‚Äôve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I‚Äôve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

snippet.description:

The film features music composed by Rohit Sower and is produced by Daali Dhananjaya.

snippet.description:
‡∞Ü‡∞∞‡±ã‡∞ó‡±ç‡∞Ø‡∞Ç, ‡∞ê‡∞∂‡±ç‡∞µ‡∞∞‡±ç‡∞Ø‡∞Ç ‡∞™‡±ç‡∞∞‡∞∏‡∞æ‡∞¶‡∞ø‡∞Ç‡∞ö‡±á ‡∞∏‡±Å‡∞¨‡±ç‡∞∞‡∞π‡±ç‡∞Æ‡∞£‡±ç‡∞Ø ‡∞∏‡∞π‡∞∏‡±ç‡∞∞‡∞®‡∞æ‡∞Æ ‡∞∏‡±ç‡∞§‡±ã‡∞§‡±ç‡∞∞‡∞Ç | Sri Subramanya Sahasranama Stotram

Experience the divine power of the Subramanya Sahasranama Stotram, containing the 1000 Names of Lord Murugan. Chanting or listening to this sacred hymn from the Skanda Purana is the ultimate remedy for all planetary afflictions.

Lord Karthikeya, also known as Shanmukha and Skanda, is the commander of the divine army. Listening to his Sahasranamam on Tuesdays (Mangalavaram) and during Shasti is widely believed to remove Kuja Dosha (Mars Affliction) and Sarpa Dosha (Snake Curse), paving the way for a happy marriage ("Kalyana Prapti") and blessed children ("Santana Prapti").

Whether you are facing legal battles, enemies, or health issues, the vibration of these 1000 names acts as a protective shield like the holy Vel. Let this Telugu Devotional Video bring the blessings of Palani Andava to your home.

Listen to the powerful Anjaneya Dandakam with Telugu lyrics, a famous Hanuman stotram dedicated to Lord Hanuman. This Hanuman devotional song is ideal for chanting, pooja, meditation and daily bhakti practice.

Anjaneya Dandakam is widely believed to remove fear, obstacles and negativity, and bring strength, courage and divine protection. Listening to Anjaneya Dandakam Telugu lyrics regularly creates positive energy and spiritual confidence. Devotees chant this powerful Hanuman stotram on Tuesday, Saturday, Hanuman Jayanti and during special Anjaneya pooja days.

This Anjaneya Dandakam Telugu devotional song is perfect for morning prayers, evening chanting, temple worship and meditation. Devotees listen to Anjaneya Dandakam for relief from problems, peace of mind and the blessings of Lord Hanuman.

snippet.title: Hawaon Ne Yeh Kaha (Lyrical Video) | Udit Narayan | Hrithik Roshan | Ameesha Patel
snippet.description:
Hawaon Ne Yeh Kaha is a soft and romantic melody sung by Udit Narayan, featuring the beautiful pairing of Hrithik Roshan and Ameesha Patel from the movie Aap Mujhe Achche Lagne Lage. 
This song captures young love, innocence, and heartfelt emotions beautifully, making it a timeless favourite for Bollywood romance lovers. 

Credits: 
Singer: Udit Narayan
Music: Rajesh Roshan
Lyrics: Dev Kohli
Movie: Aap Mujhe Achche Lagne Lage
Starring: Hrithik Roshan, Ameesha Patel
Director: Vikram Bhatt
Producer: Rohit Kumar
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 

[Nahin marna ganwara pyaar mein 

Tumse yeh kehna hai 

Tumhein bhi zinda rehna hai 

Mujhe bhi zinda rehna hai] 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil 

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil 

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Magar jo pyaar karte hain 

Kabhi bharte nahin aahein 


Hawaon ne yeh kaha 

Fizaon ne yeh kaha 

Aayi pyaar ki ye rut badi tufani 

Tu darna na o meri rani 

Badlega yeh mausam ari deewani 

Hum likhenge prem kahani 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil 

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil 

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Magar jo pyaar karte hain 

Kabhi bharte nahin aahein 

Hawaon ne yeh kaha 

Fizaon ne yeh kaha 

Aayi pyaar ki ye rut badi tufani 

Tu darna na o meri rani 

Badlega yeh mausam ari deewani 

Hum likhenge prem kahani 

Gardish mein hi sahi 

Yeh sitare humnashin 

Gardish mein hi sahi 

Yeh sitare humnashin 

Dhoondhegi kal hamein 

Phir bahaarein humnashin 

Imtehan pyaar ke roz hote nahin 

Pyaar wale kabhi sabra khote nahi 

Mohabbat ho hi jaati hai 

Mohabbat ki nahi jaati 

Yeh aisi cheez hai jo sabke 

Hisse mein nahi aati 

Hawaon ne yeh kaha 

Fizaon ne yeh kaha 

Aayi pyaar ki ye rut badi tufani 

Tu darna na o meri rani 

Badlega yeh mausam ari deewani 

Hum likhenge prem kahani 

Woh mohabbat hi nahin 

Jismein dil lut gaye 

Woh mohabbat hi nahin 

Jismein dil lut gaye 

De ke kurbaniyan premi khud mit gaye 

Soch le jaan-e-man humko milna hai abs 

Aage peechhe nahi, sath chalna hai ab 

Mohabbat raaz hai aisa 

Jo samjhaya nahi jata 

Yeh aisa geet hai har 

Saaz pe gaya nahi jata 

Hawaon ne yeh kaha 

Fizaon ne yeh kaha 

Aayi pyaar ki ye rut badi tufani 

Tu darna na o meri rani 

Badlega yeh mausam ari deewani 

Hum likhenge prem kahani 

[Hum likhenge prem kahani] (x4)
